                  "fill": "$--text-secondary",
                  "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "content": "Staff-level AI and Software Engineer specializing in production-grade AI systems for healthcare and data-intensive environments. I lead teams that build LLM-based agent workflows, RAG systems, and secure data pipelines — from architecture to deployment.",
