                  "fontWeight": "600",
                  "letterSpacing": 2
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "FPm7T",
                  "name": "p1",
                  "fill": "#94A3B8",
                  "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "content": "Built an agentic RAG (Retrieval-Augmented Generation) application using LangChain, OpenAI APIs, and vector retrieval for complex multi-step queries. The agent handles the GAIA benchmark — a challenging evaluation framework that tests AI systems on real-world tasks requiring multi-step reasoning, tool use, and knowledge retrieval.",
                  "lineHeight": 1.75,
                  "fontFamily": "Inter",
                  "fontSize": 16,
                  "fontWeight": "normal"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "yjKM2",
                  "name": "p2",
                  "fill": "#94A3B8",
                  "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "content": "Achieved a 90% score on the GAIA benchmark, earning the Top Performer certification from Hugging Face. The benchmark evaluates AI assistants on tasks that require browsing the web, analyzing documents, executing code, and combining information from multiple sources.",
                  "lineHeight": 1.75,
                  "fontFamily": "Inter",
                  "fontSize": 16,
                  "fontWeight": "normal"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "g5k24",
                  "name": "p3",
                  "fill": "#94A3B8",
                  "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "content": "Engineered a multi-tool agent architecture with robust guardrails and context management. The agent dynamically selects between document retrieval, web search, code execution, and direct reasoning. Vector retrieval enables efficient document search, while the planning module breaks complex queries into manageable sub-tasks.",
                  "lineHeight": 1.75,
                  "fontFamily": "Inter",
                  "fontSize": 16,
                  "fontWeight": "normal"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
