            {
              "type": "frame",
              "id": "o6LX8",
              "name": "Details Section",
              "width": "fill_container",
              "layout": "vertical",
              "gap": 16,
              "children": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "r2ORk",
                  "name": "detailsLabel",
                  "fill": "#FFA6CD",
                  "content": "WHAT I BUILT",
                  "fontFamily": "JetBrains Mono",
                  "fontSize": 12,
                  "fontWeight": "600",
                  "letterSpacing": 2
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "Go5f0",
                  "name": "p1",
                  "fill": "#94A3B8",
                  "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "content": "Designed and deployed a Retrieval-Augmented Generation system that enables natural language queries over internal documentation and knowledge bases. The system serves as a decision-support tool, surfacing relevant information from large and diverse document collections.",
                  "lineHeight": 1.75,
                  "fontFamily": "Inter",
                  "fontSize": 16,
                  "fontWeight": "normal"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "oGmia",
                  "name": "p2",
                  "fill": "#94A3B8",
                  "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "content": "The architecture was designed for production reliability at enterprise scale, with built-in guardrails to prevent hallucinated or off-topic responses, quality monitoring to track answer accuracy over time, and administrative controls for managing the document corpus.",
                  "lineHeight": 1.75,
                  "fontFamily": "Inter",
                  "fontSize": 16,
                  "fontWeight": "normal"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "fG6jT",
                  "name": "p3",
                  "fill": "#94A3B8",
                  "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "content": "The retrieval layer implements vector search with transformer-based embeddings and re-ranking stages. The generation component orchestrates retrieved context with prompt engineering techniques to produce accurate, grounded answers with source attribution.",
                  "lineHeight": 1.75,
                  "fontFamily": "Inter",
                  "fontSize": 16,
                  "fontWeight": "normal"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
